<ScopeNote xmlns="http://vocab.getty.edu/ontology#" rdf:about="http://vocab.getty.edu/ulan/scopeNote/124278">
	<rdf:value xml:lang="en">Prominent English naturalist and geologist known for contributions to a unifying evolutionary theory, explaining the diversity of life; laid out in the 1859 book "On the Origin of Species."</rdf:value>
